Motor Trend Car Road Tests

Source: R/mtcars.R
mtcars.Rd

Format

A data frame with 32 observations on 11 (numeric) variables:

mpg

Miles/(US) gallon.

cyl

integer. Number of cylinders.

disp

Displacement (cu.in.).

hp

Gross horsepower.

drat

Rear axle ratio.

wt

Weight (1000 lbs).

qsec

1/4 mile time.

vs

Engine (0 = V-shaped, 1 = straight).

am

Transmission (0 = automatic, 1 = manual).

gear

Number of forward gears.

carb

Number of carburetors.

@source The data is from the mtcars dataset in the link{dplyr}{mtcars} dataset.

mtcars The data was extracted from the 1974 Motor Trend US magazine, and comprises fuel consumption and 10 aspects of automobile design and performance for 32 automobiles (1973–74 models). datasets
